OL,3,CMan ordered to pay nearly #3,000 for
OL,4,Cflying drone over new stadium
OL,6,FA man has been ordered to pay just
OL,7,Funder #3,000 for flying his drone over
OL,8,Fa football stadium.
OL,10,FThe flight took place from the Wirral,
OL,11,Fcrossing the River Mersey to the new
OL,12,FEverton stadium at Bramley-Moore Dock.
OL,14,FA court heard Nicholas Durbin flew the
OL,15,Fdrone above the 400ft height limit on
OL,16,F9 May 2024, potentially endangering
OL,17,Fany other airspace users in the area.
