OL,3,CMan ordered to pay nearly #3,000 for
OL,4,Cflying drone over new stadium
OL,6,FDuring this flight the 45-year-old
OL,7,Falso travelled up to 1.3km away from
OL,8,Fhis take-off point, meaning he could
OL,9,Fnot maintain a "visual line of sight".
OL,11,FOn another occasion, on 20 March 2024,
OL,12,FDurbin also flew a drone at nearly
OL,13,F300ft above the legal height limit in
OL,14,FAnglesey.
OL,16,FDuring this flight he also travelled
OL,17,Fup to 2.39km away from his take-off
OL,18,Fpoint, meaning he again could not
OL,19,Fmaintain visual line of sight.
