OL,3,CMan ordered to pay nearly #3,000 for
OL,4,Cflying drone over new stadium
OL,6,FDurbin, of Merlin Avenue, Upton,
OL,7,FWirral, was found guilty at Sefton
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court on Thursday, 13
OL,9,FMarch 2025 on four offences: two
OL,10,Foffences of being the remote pilot of
OL,11,Fan unmanned aircraft failing to comply
OL,12,Fwith operating height and two offences
OL,13,Fof being the remote pilot of an
OL,14,Funmanned aircraft failing to keep
OL,15,Funmanned aircraft in sight.
OL,17,FHe was given a combined fine of
OL,18,F#1,600, a victim surcharge of #640 and
OL,19,Fcosts of #650, totalling #2,890.
