OL,3,CMan ordered to pay nearly #3,000 for
OL,4,Cflying drone over new stadium
OL,6,FSergeant Kyle Sayers said: "Over the
OL,7,Fcoming months Merseyside Police will
OL,8,Fbe proactively targeting illegal drone
OL,9,Fuse and during the Aintree Festival
OL,10,Fnext month a temporary restricted
OL,11,Fairspace will be in place.
OL,13,F"Merseyside Police is responsible for
OL,14,Fkeeping the public safe and airspace
OL,15,Frestrictions form part of those
OL,16,Fmeasures just like road closures or
OL,17,Friver patrols.
