OL,3,CMan ordered to pay nearly #3,000 for
OL,4,Cflying drone over new stadium
OL,6,F"We have used drone restrictions to
OL,7,Fgreat effect during past large public
OL,8,Fevents including Eurovision, Aintree
OL,9,FFestival and the visit of HMS Prince
OL,10,Fof Wales to ensure people are not in
OL,11,Fany danger, however our proactive
OL,12,Fapproach will not only target
OL,13,Frestricted airspace, as this
OL,14,Fprosecution shows.
OL,16,F"Drone users who fly inside a
OL,17,Frestricted airspace that have not been
OL,18,Fgranted permission will be guilty of
OL,19,Fcommitting an offence and could be
OL,20,Fprosecuted as well as having their
OL,21,Fequipment seized and confiscated."
